  <entry>
    <title>资料分析-增长率、增长量</title>
    <url>/post/%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E7%8E%87%E5%92%8C%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E9%87%8F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1>增长率</h1>
<h2 id="一般增长率">一般增长率</h2>
<h3 id="百分数与百分点">百分数与百分点</h3>
<p><img src="https://80af204.webp.li/2024/12/7324d18d60dcff636a332f2f10c02307.png" alt="image-20241203225401145"></p>
<h3 id="“增长率”与“倍数”">“增长率”与“倍数”</h3>
<ul>
<li>倍数 = <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mtext>现期</mtext><mtext>基期</mtext></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac{现期}{基期}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.2173em;vertical-align:-0.345em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8723em;"><span style="top:-2.655em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord cjk_fallback mtight">基期</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.394em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord cjk_fallback mtight">现期</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.345em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span>             增长率 = 倍数 = <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mtext>现期</mtext><mo>−</mo><mtext>基期</mtext></mrow><mtext>基期</mtext></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac{现期-基期}{基期}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.2173em;vertical-align:-0.345em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8723em;"><span style="top:-2.655em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord cjk_fallback mtight">基期</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.394em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord cjk_fallback mtight">现期</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback mtight">基期</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.345em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><mark> 两者的关系：增长率 = 倍数 - 1 </mark></p>
<h3 id="“成数”、“翻番”">“成数”、“翻番”</h3>
<p><mark> 成数 </mark>：几成相当于十分之几</p>
<p><mark> 翻番 </mark>：翻一番为原来的2倍；翻两番为原来的4倍；以此类推，翻n番为原来的2^n^倍</p>
<h3 id="“增幅”、“降幅”、“变化幅度”">“增幅”、“降幅”、“变化幅度”</h3>
<p><mark>增幅（就是增长率）</mark>：可升可降，带符号比</p>
<p><mark>降幅</mark>：看下降的，比绝对值</p>
<p><mark>变化幅度</mark>：可升可降，比绝对值</p>
<h3 id="高减低加-扩大减、收窄加">高减低加 = 扩大减、收窄加</h3>
<p><img src="https://80af204.webp.li/2024/12/eb755f01fb739872d9ed87a07f3f2f41.png" alt="image-20241203232010827"></p>
<h2 id="增长率的计算">增长率的计算</h2>
<p>识别：问增长率/增速，增长/下降+%（选项）</p>
<p>公式：r = <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mtext>增长量</mtext><mtext>基期量</mtext></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac{增长量}{基期量}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.2173em;vertical-align:-0.345em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8723em;"><span style="top:-2.655em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord cjk_fallback mtight">基期量</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.394em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord cjk_fallback mtight">增长量</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.345em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span> = <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mtext>增长量</mtext><mrow><mtext>现期</mtext><mo>−</mo><mtext>增长量</mtext></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac{增长量}{现期-增长量}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.2757em;vertical-align:-0.4033em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vli